				<wikidot:authorName>Scorpion451</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1918720</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Same here- it just doesn't ever click for me. Which is strange, because I generally enjoy Kalinin's stuff.</p> <p>@ Kalinin: After thinking on this for a while, I think what I'm missing here is your usual &quot;wheels within wheels&quot; complexity and rich detail, which I really enjoy as a reader. It feels kind of like having a sandwich at a restaurant where you usually get a double decker cheeseburger with everything on it, if that makes sense.</p> 
				 	]]>
