					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1758441#post-2536601</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1758441/scp-2529#post-2536601</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 12 Jul 2016 07:57:13 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Dr Hush</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1701286</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The phrase &quot;SCP-2529 occurrence&quot; is used several times, and it's confusing because it could refer to the unsolved murder, <em>or</em> the anomalous phenomenon affecting information about it.</p> <p>Why not designate the <em>occurance</em> SCP-2529-1?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
